menu "Utest Framework"

config RT_UTEST_SELF_PASS
    bool "UTEST Framework Test"
    select RT_USING_UTEST
    default n
    help
        RT_UTEST_SELF_PASS controls whether the Utest framework's self-test functionality is enabled.    
        Once enabled, RT_USING_UTEST will be enabled automatically, and the self-test code included with the Utest framework will also be compiled.

        Application scenario: 
        Verifying whether the Utest framework functions correctly.
endmenu
